GitHub

{r github push}
CommitMessage <- paste("updated on ", Sys.time(), sep = "")
wd <- getwd()
gitCommand <- paste("cd ", 
                    wd,
                    " \n git add . \n git commit --message '",
                    CommitMessage,
                    "' \n git push origin master \n",
                    sep = ""
                    )
system(command = gitCommand,
       intern = TRUE
)
